		<h2><a href="http://maybemaimed.com/2011/12/04/on-being-bondage-furniture/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to On Being Bondage Furniture">On Being Bondage Furniture</a></h2>
		<div class="col140 postInfos">
			<p><strong>04 Dec 2011</strong> at 16:09</p>
			<p><strong>maymay</strong></p>
			<p><a href="http://maybemaimed.com/label/bitter-and-jealous/" title="View all posts in Bitter and jealous" rel="category tag">Bitter and jealous</a>, <a href="http://maybemaimed.com/label/emotions/" title="View all posts in Emotions" rel="category tag">Emotions</a>, <a href="http://maybemaimed.com/label/personal-experience/" title="View all posts in Personal experience" rel="category tag">Personal experience</a>, <a href="http://maybemaimed.com/label/personal-history/" title="View all posts in Personal history" rel="category tag">Personal history</a>, <a href="http://maybemaimed.com/label/politics-of-sex/" title="View all posts in Politics of sex" rel="category tag">Politics of sex</a></p>
